data.title: Paris 2024: GB's Jade Jones interview after shock taekwondo exit
data.meta_description: GB's double Olympic taekwondo champion Jade Jones says she is "devastated" after a shock-first round exit at Paris 2024 to Macedonia's Miljana Reljikj.
